I/flutter ( 3162): TextEditingController#9066a(TextEditingValue(text: ┤000├, selection: TextSelection(baseOffset: 3, extentOffset: 3, affinity: TextAffinity.downstream, isDirectional: false), composing: TextRange(start: -1, end: -1)))
