I was able to reproduce part of this issue on latest master channel.



> * on the first input, the listener is called twice

I can't reproduce this on `master` channel. What is happening is that the first print happens when the TextFormField gains focus.


> when the controller is cleared, the listener is called 3 times.
> * one with the empty text
> * one with the previous text
> * the last with the empty text again.

This may be eventually caused because you're clearing the field inside the listener. I added a delay in the clear operation with a duration of one second and here is my output (the first line is when the field gains focus):

```
flutter: TextEditingController#87c5c(TextEditingValue(text: ┤├, selection: TextSelection(baseOffset: 0, extentOffset: 0, affinity: TextAffinity.downstream, isDirectional: false), composing: TextRange(start: -1, end: -1)))
flutter: TextEditingController#87c5c(TextEditingValue(text: ┤q├, selection: TextSelection(baseOffset: 1, extentOffset: 1, affinity: TextAffinity.downstream, isDirectional: false), composing: TextRange(start: -1, end: -1)))
flutter: TextEditingController#87c5c(TextEditingValue(text: ┤qw├, selection: TextSelection(baseOffset: 2, extentOffset: 2, affinity: TextAffinity.downstream, isDirectional: false), composing: TextRange(start: -1, end: -1)))
flutter: TextEditingController#87c5c(TextEditingValue(text: ┤qwe├, selection: TextSelection(baseOffset: 3, extentOffset: 3, affinity: TextAffinity.downstream, isDirectional: false), composing: TextRange(start: -1, end: -1)))
flutter: TextEditingController#87c5c(TextEditingValue(text: ┤├, selection: TextSelection(baseOffset: -1, extentOffset: -1, affinity: TextAffinity.downstream, isDirectional: false), composing: TextRange(start: -1, end: -1)))
flutter: TextEditingController#87c5c(TextEditingValue(text: ┤├, selection: TextSelection(baseOffset: 0, extentOffset: 0, affinity: TextAffinity.downstream, isDirectional: false), composing: TextRange(start: -1, end: -1)))
```

Note that after cleaning the field I got two prints, this may be the issue: the listener is being called multiple times when we call `controller.clear()`.

<details>
<summary> complete sample code (with a delay before cleaning the text field)</summary>

```
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

